com.panacea.sdk.model
Class PMDictionary

java.lang.Object
  com.panacea.sdk.model.PMDictionary

public class PMDictionary
extends java.lang.Object

Inspired by iOS NSDictionary, contains key-value pairs. Used in PANACEA API web calls. The key is a parameter name (String) and the value may be one of the following types:

  • String
  • boolean
  • int
  • long
  • double
  • PMDictionary
  • PMArray

Cobi Interactive
